    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-05-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-05-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="76"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d76">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Adams.</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 1984.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<hi rend="italic">
                                Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-05-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 17, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I transmit a letter of the 13th instant from
                    James Rogers, of No. 8 Wall street, New York, and the original depositions which
                    accompanied it, relative to the case of William Jackson, otherwise called John
                    McCafferty, reported to be under sentence of death for high treason in
                    Ireland.</p>
                <p>You will make the most effective use of them you can, in using your good offices
                    on behalf of the prisoner to obtain his release or a mitigation of his
                    sentence.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles Francis Adams</hi>, Esq., <hi rend="italic"
                            >&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
